rows.label: qst202004_msg001
rows.name:
Don't suppose Musubi'll notice if
I have a quick nibble while she's
in the kitchen...

rows.label: qst202004_msg003
rows.name: You heard none of that! You hear?

rows.label: qst202004_msg101
rows.name: They sell Bitter Choclit in Fons Maim.

rows.label: qst202004_msg102
rows.name:
But you don't see many Fruity Rice
Balls nowadays.

rows.label: qst202004_msg103
rows.name:
When I was a lad, you used to
be able to get 'em all over
Gula and Avaritia.

rows.label: qst202004_msg104
rows.name:
Well, you never know, maybe
they'll have a resurgence once
trade improves.
